Package: mastodon-image-poster
Architecture: all
Multi-Arch: foreign
Depends:
 ${misc:Depends},
 python3,
 python3-mastodon
Description: Daily automatic image posting to Mastodon
 A systemd timer-driven service that posts one image per day from a
 configured directory to a Mastodon instance. Supports sorting by
 filename, file size or creation time. Tracks state to resume after
 restart without re-posting already sent images.
